en_52592_0	Visiting UK Minister Alistair Burt who delivered a guest lecture at the Lakshman Kadirgamar Institute for International Relations and Strategic Studies yesterday has urged the Sri Lankan government to invite UN High Commissioner of Human Rights Navaneethan Pillai to visit the island.
en_52592_1	Delivering his oration at the Lakshman Kadiragarmer Institute yesterday Burt stressed that transparency between all parties was the only way to foster understanding.
en_52592_2	Accordingly he had also noted that Sri Lanka should take steps to further extend this investigation to other UN rapporteurs as well.
